              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="border-b border-indigo-100 pb-4">
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">How long does shipping take?</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Standard shipping: 3-5 business days. Express: 1-2 business days.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Do you offer international shipping?</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Yes! We ship to over 50 countries worldwide.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <a
            href="/pages/faq"
            class="inline-block mt-6 text-indigo-600 font-medium hover:text-indigo-800 transition-colors duration-300 flex items-center gap-2"
          >
            View all FAQs
            <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i>
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Store Hours -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-8">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Customer Support Hours</h3>
          <div class="space-y-3">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
              <span class="text-gray-700">Monday - Friday</span>
              <span class="font-semibold text-gray-900">9:00 AM - 6:00 PM EST</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
              <span class="text-gray-700">Saturday</span>
              <span class="font-semibold text-gray-900">10:00 AM - 4:00 PM EST</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
              <span class="text-gray-700">Sunday</span>
              <span class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Closed</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-6">* Holiday hours may vary. We respond to emails 24/7.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Social Media -->
    <div class="mt-20 text-center">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">Connect With Us</h3>
      <div class="flex justify-center gap-6">
        <a
          href="#"
          class="w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-gray-900 text-white flex items-center justify-center text-xl hover:bg-gray-800 transition-colors duration-300 hover:scale-110"
        >
          <i class="fab fa-instagram"></i>
        </a>
        <a
          href="#"
          class="w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-gray-900 text-white flex items-center justify-center text-xl hover:bg-gray-800 transition-colors duration-300 hover:scale-110"
        >
          <i class="fab fa-facebook-f"></i>
        </a>
        <a
          href="#"
          class="w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-gray-900 text-white flex items-center justify-center text-xl hover:bg-gray-800 transition-colors duration-300 hover:scale-110"
        >
          <i class="fab fa-tiktok"></i>
        </a>
        <a
          href="#"
          class="w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-gray-900 text-white flex items-center justify-center text-xl hover:bg-gray-800 transition-colors duration-300 hover:scale-110"
        >
          <i class="fab fa-pinterest-p"></i>
        </a>
      </div>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mt-6 max-w-md mx-auto">Follow us for styling tips, new arrivals, and exclusive offers.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

